td.p:
This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Article 45(2)(c) and (g) and Article 45(3)(a) of Directive 2004/18/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 31 March 2004 on the coordination of procedures for the award of public works contracts, public supply contracts and public service contracts (
OJ 2004 L 134, p. 114
) and of certain general principles of EU law.
